---
---

<section
  aria-labelledby="probleem-heading"
  style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #141422 100%); color: white; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 110px 24px;"
>
  <!-- Dot grid background -->
  <div aria-hidden="true" style="position: absolute; inset: 0; opacity: 0.03; background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(46,204,113,0.5) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px; pointer-events: none;"></div>

  <!-- Morph blob -->
  <div class="morph-blob" aria-hidden="true" style="position: absolute; width: 400px; height: 400px; top: -10%; right: -5%; background: var(--color-accent); opacity: 0.04; pointer-events: none;"></div>

  <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative;">

    <!-- Section label -->
    <div class="reveal" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
      <div style="width: 28px; height: 1.5px; background: var(--color-accent);"></div>
      <span style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--color-accent); text-transform: uppercase;">Herkenbaar?</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Heading -->
    <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1" id="probleem-heading" style="font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 44px); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 64px; max-width: 600px; color: white;">
      Terwijl jij behandelt, loopt de agenda van je concurrent vol.
      <span style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); font-style: italic; font-weight: 400;"> Niet door beter te zijn.</span>
    </h2>

    <!-- Three problem items — vertical list with connectors -->
    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="display: flex; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 48px; align-items: flex-start; padding-left: 8px;">
      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
        <div style="width: 3px; height: 3px; border-radius: 50%; background: #ef4444; box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(239,68,68,0.6); margin-top: 12px;"></div>
        <div style="width: 1px; height: 48px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); margin-top: 12px;"></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); letter-spacing: 0.08em;">01</span>
        <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: white; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Je bent onzichtbaar</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); max-width: 480px; margin: 0;">
          Patiënten zoeken op 'fysiotherapeut' + jouw stad. Jij staat niet op pagina 1. Je concurrent wel — alleen omdat diens profiel completer is.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3" style="display: flex; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 48px; align-items: flex-start; padding-left: 8px;">
      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
        <div style="width: 3px; height: 3px; border-radius: 50%; background: #f59e0b; box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(245,158,11,0.5); margin-top: 12px;"></div>
        <div style="width: 1px; height: 48px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); margin-top: 12px;"></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); letter-spacing: 0.08em;">02</span>
        <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: white; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Je concurrent profiteert daarvan</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); max-width: 480px; margin: 0;">
          Ze zijn niet beter dan jij. Ze worden alleen beter gevonden. Betere foto's, meer reviews, een compleet profiel. Patiënten kiezen wat ze kunnen vinden.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-4" style="display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: flex-start; padding-left: 8px;">
      <div style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 12px; width: 3px; height: 3px; border-radius: 50%; background: #ef4444; box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(239,68,68,0.6);"></div>
      <div>
        <span style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); letter-spacing: 0.08em;">03</span>
        <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: white; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Elke dag verlies je patiënten</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); max-width: 480px; margin: 0;">
          Dit is geen toekomstig probleem. Het gebeurt nu. Elke dag zoeken mensen in jouw regio naar een fysiotherapeut — en bellen iemand anders.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CountUp stats block -->
    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-5" style="margin-top: 64px; display: flex; gap: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap; padding: 32px; border-radius: 16px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
      <div>
        <div style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--color-accent);">
          <span
            data-count-up
            data-target="97"
            data-suffix="%"
            class="count-up-target"
          >97%</span>
        </div>
        <div style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top: 4px;">zoekt online naar een fysiotherapeut</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: white;">
          <span
            data-count-up
            data-target="10350"
            class="count-up-target"
          >10.350</span>
        </div>
        <div style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top: 4px;">fysiotherapiepraktijken in Nederland</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">
          9 op 10
        </div>
        <div style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top: 4px;">leest reviews voor het kiezen</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
